<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>

<title>Style Sheet Example</title>

<style>

body{

font-family:Segoe UI;

background:
linear-gradient(
135deg,
#1e3c72,
#2a5298
);

color:white;

text-align:center;

padding:50px;
}

.container{

width:600px;

margin:auto;

padding:30px;

background:
rgba(255,255,255,.15);

border-radius:15px;

backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
}

button{

padding:12px 25px;

background:#00E5FF;

border:none;

border-radius:8px;

cursor:pointer;

font-weight:bold;
}

button:hover{

background:white;

color:#000;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>CSS Style Sheet Demo</h1>

<p>
This webpage demonstrates the use of
Internal Cascading Style Sheets (CSS).
</p>

<button>
Learn More
</button>

</div>

</body>
</html>
